		"description": "<p>Starting at 14th level, your experience in battle lets you help your companions more easily. You can use the Help action as a bonus action. In addition,&nbsp;when you take the Help action choose one of the following effects:</p><ul><li>You end the frightened condition on one creature within 30 feet of you that can hear or see you.</li><li>You grant one creature within 5 feet of you temporary hit points equal to your Charisma modifier.</li><li>You touch a living creature that has 0 hit points. The creature regains 1 hit point.</li></ul>",
